item.title: CVE-2022-26100|2024-08-03T04:56:37.455Z -- sap%20se -- sapcar
item.description: SAPCAR - version 7.22, does not contain sufficient input validation on the SAPCAR archive. As a result, the SAPCAR process may crash, and the attacker may obtain privileged access to the system.
